        Yellow vs red was not enough on its own: testers asked which one
        was urgent. The strings now carry the severity in WORDS too:
            "available"  = soft hint (yellow), link still works
            "required"   = blocking (red), HUD has dropped wire frames
        and EACH names which side the rider needs to update.
    -->
